    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，E是执行器控制器的入口。然后要经过F和G两个中间处理节点，最后到H。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
